# Sercos III AT0 (Acknowledge Telegram, telegram 0) carrying the Master Sync Telegram (MST), phase CP2.
# EtherType 0x88CD. Byte0=0x60 (P-Telegram, AT, CycleCountValid, telegram 0), byte1=0x02 (Phase CP2),
# CRC32=0xefcdab90 (little-endian on wire). Hand-constructed and verified with tshark (frame.protocols
# = eth:ethertype:siii; dissects as AT0 / MST / Phase CP2).
